      • IntegerIndividual

        public IntegerIndividual(int length,
                 int min,
                 int max)
        Creates an individual of specified length with the specified limits. The genes are uninitialized.
        Parameters:
        length - The length of the individual.
        min - The minimum value in the individual.
        max - The upper limit of the value of the individual (the maximum gene will be max - 1)
